What to Do after installing Fedora 24 

sudo dnf update


rpm Repo
sudo dnf install --nogpgcheck http://download1.rpmfusion.org/free/fedora/rpmfusion-free-release-24.noarch.rpm
sudo dnf install --nogpgcheck http://download1.rpmfusion.org/nonfree/fedora/rpmfusion-nonfree-release-24.noarch.rpm

Redshift For your Eyes
sudo dnf install redshift

If you on gnome 
sudo dnf install gnome-tweak-tool

To install kde desktop
dnf install @kde-desktop

TO install cinnamon desktop
dnf install @cinnamon-desktop

To install mate desktop
dnf install @mate-desktop

TO install Xfce desktop 
dnf install @xfce-desktop

To install Steam 
dnf config-manager --add-repo=http://negativo17.org/repos/fedora-steam.repo
dnf install steam



To install Nvidia drivers
dnf update
restart
dnf install kernel-devel
dnf config-manager --add-repo=http://negativo17.org/repos/fedora-nvidia.repo
dnf install nvidia-driver dkms-nvidia

